metadata.name: Starlight Warrior
metadata.description:
The Ninja at stary night who saves stars known as Starlight warriors from black forest and they turn into bright stars, like stars of the galaxy, the ninja starlight are not like ordinary star warriors. they are hard ,powerful. There is a lot of magic power in them. Even the most powerful in the all galaxies. 

Canvas size -  2000×2500  
Size - 3.94 Mb
